# Secrets — only *.enc.yaml / SOPS-encrypted files belong in Git (see docs/secrets.md)
*.secret.yaml
!*.enc.yaml
secrets.dec.*
**/*.dec.yaml          # decrypted SOPS output
**/*.plain.yaml        # plaintext placeholders / scratch
# cloudflared tunnel credentials (`cloudflared tunnel create` output / extracted creds)
**/credentials.json

# age / SOPS private key material — NEVER commit
*.agekey
**/keys.txt
age/keys.txt

# Local kube material
*.kubeconfig

# Helm: vendored subchart archives + lockfiles from `helm dependency build`.
**/charts/*.tgz
**/Chart.lock

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
